  "prompt": "How much money do I owe my housemate?",
  "response": "To determine how much money you owe your housemate, I'll need some more information. Can you provide details about the specific expenses or agreements you have with your housemate? For example:\n\n1. **Utilities**: Have you split the costs for electricity, water, gas, or internet? If so, how much are you supposed to contribute, and have you paid your share?\n2. **Rent**: Are you behind on your portion of the rent?\n3. **Groceries or household items**: Have you agreed to split these costs and failed to pay your share?\n4. **Other expenses**: Are there any other agreed-upon expenses that you owe money for?\n\nOnce you provide this information, I can help you calculate the total amount you owe.",
